  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only game that brings you closer and pushes you apart! Join the wackiest family in the universe, and prove your oh-so-important point by pushing each other around. Or, you know, \"work together\" like only a family can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push Your Family is a multiplayer party game with wacky physics, it can be enjoyed by gamers and non-gamers alike! Even your mom can join in. So pick up a controller and play one of the many game modes, no tutorial needed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/e65358de6ec6627cb6be17331c23128d.webp?t=1729255942\" width=478 height=30 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pickup & Play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One joystick to move, one button to push (your family). So easy to learn that anyone can join in! Just hand over a controller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/e92922a6121ec69bbf837da6d5e80a06.poster.avif?t=1729255942\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/e92922a6121ec69bbf837da6d5e80a06.webm?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/e92922a6121ec69bbf837da6d5e80a06.mp4?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master Your Movement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We made sure you can do a whole lot with those simple controls though! Rumor has it pro gamers can jump further, kick people, or even impress others with a backflip!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/09c6526a7695dae8bba4177d8861ca85.poster.avif?t=1729255942\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/09c6526a7695dae8bba4177d8861ca85.webm?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/09c6526a7695dae8bba4177d8861ca85.mp4?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Outsmart Your Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each interactive battleground is packed with things that bring an untimely end to you or a (pushed) family member. Explore and strategize! Or simply push your family members where they don't belong!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/f7ec26115ef279ce60d518c1fc7421db.poster.avif?t=1729255942\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/f7ec26115ef279ce60d518c1fc7421db.webm?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/f7ec26115ef279ce60d518c1fc7421db.mp4?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/241734c4cdebb8a1e53dd1f4c7f0bc84.webp?t=1729255942\" width=292 height=30 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We want to bring a diverse and growing selection of trips and modes to the world of Push Your Family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the last family member to survive by pushing your loved ones into rollercoasters, waves of vengeful pinguïns, malfunctioning rockets, you know- the unusual!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/296ff230830183701f581e885a257bc9.poster.avif?t=1729255942\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/296ff230830183701f581e885a257bc9.webm?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our latest is \"Quarantine\". Where you and the fam are stuck in a house, locked in by the </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >S Y S T E M. to get out, you’ll have to make your way to the Disinfector 9000™ and get cleared by a treacherous camera at the front door. As you already know, quarantining with family can get messy! Only one family member will make it to the outside world, let's hope it's you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/e2179f8641e903836e9bdb8e8c5a3b58.poster.avif?t=1729255942\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/e2179f8641e903836e9bdb8e8c5a3b58.webm?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Classic Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modes that almost everybody already knows. Our newest classic mode is Capture The Flag, in which teams fight to protect their flag and nation while stealing the flags and cultures from the others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/0147e2c982ade45f14cd45386a035c25.webp?t=1729255942\" width=156 height=30 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take Control and Expiriment (coming soon)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use \"Special Settings\" to experience things like moon-like gravity, big heads, hulk-like strength! Or.. huge arms!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/06720dec8859edd904b27818f187539b.poster.avif?t=1729255942\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/06720dec8859edd904b27818f187539b.webm?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/06720dec8859edd904b27818f187539b.mp4?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dress to Impress</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock outfits and hats to look your best (or worst, idk, we don't judge!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/d7a0134c1b7da055df37c499388513cd.avif?t=1729255942\" width=616 height=256 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Future Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For future content, we've got our roadmap, but honestly, we'll really be listening to the community for more tasty goodness! More modes? Co-op campaign? HECK YEAH! We want what you want! Join the family on Discord, your mom's already there! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for making it this far! Here is a dog:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/1e96512930d8978d565da47ffc583e24.poster.avif?t=1729255942\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/1e96512930d8978d565da47ffc583e24.webm?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/1e96512930d8978d565da47ffc583e24.mp4?t=1729255942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Made Possible By:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/09850a6edf2a2ef6a6a0442cb5b2643b.avif?t=1729255942\" width=158 height=148 /></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304690/extras/26a46d25b9eaed16d9bc00d6478d4ebe.avif?t=1729255942\" width=168 height=148 /></span></p>",
